# Current Project APIs

## 🔓 Public Endpoints
- `GET /jobs` - Browse all jobs
- `GET /company` - View approved companies

## 🔐 Auth Endpoints (`/auth`)
- `POST /auth/register` - Register (CANDIDATE or EMPLOYER)
- `POST /auth/login` - Login -> returns JWT

## 👤 Candidate Endpoints (`/candidate`)
- `POST /candidate/profile` - Create candidate profile
- `PUT /candidate/profile/{profileId}` - Update candidate profile
- `POST /candidate/resume` - Upload resume (PDF, multipart)
- `POST /candidate/jobs/{jobId}/apply` - Apply to a job

## 🏢 Employer Endpoints (`/employer`)
- `POST /employer/profile` - Create company profile
- `PUT /employer/profile/{companyId}` - Update company profile
- `POST /employer/jobs/{companyId}` - Post a new job
- `GET /employer/jobs` - View all posted jobs
- `PUT /employer/jobs/{companyId}/{jobId}` - Edit a job post
- `DELETE /employer/jobs/{companyId}/{jobId}` - Delete a job post
- `GET /employer/jobs/{jobId}/applicants` - View applicants for a job
- `PUT /employer/jobs/{jobId}/applicants/{applicationId}` - Update application status

## 🛡️ Admin Endpoints (`/admin`)
- `GET /admin/all-users` - List all users
- `GET /admin/all-companies` - List all approved companies
- `GET /admin/companies/pending` - View all companies pending approval
- `PUT /admin/companies/{companyId}/approve` - Approve a company
- `PUT /admin/companies/{companyId}/reject` - Reject a company
- `GET /admin/jobs/pending` - View all jobs pending approval
- `PUT /admin/jobs/{jobId}/approve` - Approve a job post
- `PUT /admin/jobs/{jobId}/reject` - Reject a job post
- `GET /admin/users` - (Current is `/admin/users`)

